freenet.store.saltedhash
Class SaltedHashFreenetStore<T extends StorableBlock>

java.lang.Object
  freenet.store.saltedhash.SaltedHashFreenetStore<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
FreenetStore<T>
public class SaltedHashFreenetStore<T extends StorableBlock>
extends Object
implements FreenetStore<T>

Index-less data store based on salted hash. Provide a pseudo-random replacement based on a salt value generated on create. Keys are check against a bloom filter before probing. Data are encrypted using the route key and the salt, so there is no way to recover the data without holding the route key. (For debugging, you can set OPTION_SAVE_PLAINKEY=true in source code)

Author:
sdiz
